{"tid":505340,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！樂視香港申請清盤 ！","createTime":"2017-12-21T04:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T12:32:47.000Z","uid":4661,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9186267d9c6b88280eed266d93c55bb3997e5439","tid":505340,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:19:58.000Z","msg":"終於收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n據法庭文件顯示，樂視香港已入紙申請清盤。<br />\n<br />\n內地網絡巨頭樂視自2015年攻港，在香港成立LeSports HK樂視體育。其後投得香港英超及NBA (於OTT平台) 等賽事之獨家播映權。不過，近期多次傳出資金鏈斷裂，今次樂視香港申請清盤，未知英超轉播權會否受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n今年11月，樂視體育出售世界盃播映權予電盈（0008）旗下的nowtv及viutv，至本月初則傳出樂視體育裁員200人。"},{"pid":"60ec54614b5d0591bfdd5d6e06e3ccd4304dce72","tid":505340,"uid":77104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"英超點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d975c6a0724397071df701ce218d3bdaed87a402","tid":505340,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英超點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾now繼續播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d999b43f5f71a56c2d7487a3b8252961878c065","tid":505340,"uid":159054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>英超點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾now繼續播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買左幾十年plan點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c949c0f9a2136c4f4b3ff70525daf4276529a6","tid":505340,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.cool-gif.com/media/gif/3c/dd/3cdda5e9124a7a6cbb089259fe62d94c/cool.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/th